snippet.title: CookieRun: OvenSmash Teaser
snippet.description:
A sneak peak into Cookie Run's first ever action-packed 3D game, OvenSmash!
Don't forget to like, subscribe, and show your love in the comments if you want more! 

쿠키런 최초의 3D 액션 게임 오븐스매시!
많은 관심과 함께 좋아요, 구독, 댓글 부탁드립니다.

Official Community
▶ Official site: https://www.ovensmash.com
▶ Official twitter: https://twitter.com/CROvenSmash
